videos.headline: UNLV strikes first on QB scramble
videos.description: Rebels QB Armani Rogers runs it up the middle and scores a 7-yard touchdown to put UNLV on the board.

videos.headline: Rebels QB Rogers rushes in for 2nd TD of game
videos.description: Armani Rogers scores with his legs again, reaching the end zone from 7 yards out to give UNLV a  14-3 lead.

videos.headline: UNLV's Kalili ejected for targeting
videos.description: Jocquez Kalili is ejected from the game after delivering a vicious late hit on San Jose State WR Malike Roberson.

videos.headline: UNLV's Presley turns on the jets
videos.description: Rebels QB Armani Rogers throws a short swing pass to Brandon Presley who turns the corner and outruns the defense to score a 44-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: San Jose State scores just before the half
videos.description: With less than 10 seconds remaining in the half, Spartans QB Josh Love finds JaQuan Blackwell in the end zone for an 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Rebels' Scissum makes leaping INT
videos.description: UNLV DB Chauncey Scissum cuts in front of the receiver's route and jumps up to pick off Josh Love's pass.

videos.headline: UNLV converts at the goal line
videos.description: On third-and-goal from the 1-yard line, Armani Rogers drops back and finds Trevor Kanteman at the goal line for a touchdown, putting the Rebels ahead 41-13.

videos.headline: Spartans' Love picked off in the end zone
videos.description: Josh Love airs out a pass to the end zone, but Jericho Flowers makes an acrobatic play to secure an interception.

videos.headline: UNLV recovers fumble at the goal line
videos.description: Rebels LB Gabe McCoy rips the ball away from Tyler Nevens at the goal line and Salanoa-Alo Wily recovers the fumble for UNLV.

videos.headline: Rogers airs it out for big UNLV gain
videos.description: Backed up against the end zone, Armani Rogers throws it deep and connects with Devonte Boyd for a 53-yard pickup.

videos.headline: UNLV routs San Jose State
videos.description: Tom Ramsey and Roy Philpott break down UNLV's 41-13 victory over San Jose State in the Rebels' conference opener.
